    {
      "brief": "Scroll style parameters",
      "fields": [
        {
          "doc": "Multiplier for free inertion. Default: 0",
          "isOptional": false,
          "name": "FRICT",
          "types": [
            "number|nil",
          ],
        },
        {
          "doc": "Multiplier for inertion, while touching. Default: 0",
          "isOptional": false,
          "name": "FRICT_HOLD",
          "types": [
            "number|nil",
          ],
        },
        {
          "doc": "Scroll speed to stop inertion. Default: 3",
          "isOptional": false,
          "name": "INERT_THRESHOLD",
          "types": [
            "number|nil",
          ],
        },
        {
          "doc": "Multiplier for inertion speed. Default: 30",
          "isOptional": false,
          "name": "INERT_SPEED",
          "types": [
            "number|nil",
          ],
        },
        {
          "doc": "Speed to check points of interests in no_inertion mode. Default: 20",
          "isOptional": false,
          "name": "POINTS_DEADZONE",
          "types": [
            "number|nil",
          ],
        },
        {
          "doc": "Scroll back returning lerp speed. Default: 35",
          "isOptional": false,
          "name": "BACK_SPEED",
          "types": [
            "number|nil",
          ],
        },
        {
          "doc": "Scroll gui.animation speed for scroll_to function. Default: 2",
          "isOptional": false,
          "name": "ANIM_SPEED",
          "types": [
            "number|nil",
          ],
        },
        {
          "doc": "extra size in pixels outside of scroll (stretch effect). Default: 0",
          "isOptional": false,
          "name": "EXTRA_STRETCH_SIZE",
          "types": [
            "number|nil",
          ],
        },
        {
          "doc": "If true, content node with size less than view node size can be scrolled. Default: false",
          "isOptional": false,
          "name": "SMALL_CONTENT_SCROLL",
          "types": [
            "boolean|nil",
          ],
        },
        {
          "doc": "The scroll speed via mouse wheel scroll or touchpad. Set to 0 to disable wheel scrolling. Default: 0",
          "isOptional": false,
          "name": "WHEEL_SCROLL_SPEED",
          "types": [
            "number|nil",
          ],
        },
        {
          "doc": "If true, invert direction for touchpad and mouse wheel scroll. Default: false",
          "isOptional": false,
          "name": "WHEEL_SCROLL_INVERTED",
          "types": [
            "boolean|nil",
          ],
        },
        {
          "doc": "If true, wheel will add inertion to scroll. Direct set position otherwise.. Default: false",
          "isOptional": false,
          "name": "WHEEL_SCROLL_BY_INERTION",
          "types": [
            "boolean|nil",
          ],
        },
      ],
      "generics": [],
      "methods": [],
      "name": "druid.scroll.style",
    },
    {
      "brief": 
"Basic Druid scroll component. Handles all scrolling behavior in Druid GUI.

### Setup
Create scroll component with druid: \`druid:new_scroll(view_node, content_node)\`

### Notes
- View_node is the static part that captures user input and recognizes scrolling touches
- Content_node is the dynamic part that will change position according to the scroll system
- Initial scroll size will be equal to content_node size
- The initial view box will be equal to view_node size
- Scroll by default style has inertia and extra size for stretching effect
- You can setup "points of interest" to make scroll always center on closest point
- Scroll events:
-   - on_scroll(self, position): On scroll move callback
-   - on_scroll_to(self, position, is_instant): On scroll_to function callback
-   - on_point_scroll(self, item_index, position): On scroll_to_index function callback
- Multitouch is required for scroll. Scroll correctly handles touch_id swap while dragging"
,
      "extends": "druid.component",
      "fields": [
        {
          "doc": "The root node",
          "isOptional": false,
          "name": "node",
          "types": [
            "node",
          ],
        },
        {
          "doc": "Optional click zone to restrict scroll area",
          "isOptional": false,
          "name": "click_zone",
          "types": [
            "node|nil",
          ],
        },
        {
          "doc": "fun(self: druid.scroll, position: vector3) Triggered on scroll move",
          "isOptional": false,
          "name": "on_scroll",
          "types": [
            "event",
          ],
        },
        {
          "doc": "fun(self: druid.scroll, target: vector3, is_instant: boolean) Triggered on scroll_to",
          "isOptional": false,
          "name": "on_scroll_to",
          "types": [
            "event",
          ],
        },
        {
          "doc": "fun(self: druid.scroll, index: number, point: vector3) Triggered on scroll_to_index",
          "isOptional": false,
          "name": "on_point_scroll",
          "types": [
            "event",
          ],
        },
        {
          "doc": "The scroll view node (static part)",
          "isOptional": false,
          "name": "view_node",
          "types": [
            "node",
          ],
        },
        {
          "doc": "The scroll view borders",
          "isOptional": false,
          "name": "view_border",
          "types": [
            "vector4",
          ],
        },
        {
          "doc": "The scroll content node (moving part)",
          "isOptional": false,
          "name": "content_node",
          "types": [
            "node",
          ],
        },
        {
          "doc": "Size of the view node",
          "isOptional": false,
          "name": "view_size",
          "types": [
            "vector3",
          ],
        },
        {
          "doc": "Current scroll position",
          "isOptional": false,
          "name": "position",
          "types": [
            "vector3",
          ],
        },
        {
          "doc": "Target scroll position for animations",
          "isOptional": false,
          "name": "target_position",
          "types": [
            "vector3",
          ],
        },
        {
          "doc": "Available content position (min_x, max_y, max_x, min_y)",
          "isOptional": false,
          "name": "available_pos",
          "types": [
            "vector4",
          ],
        },
        {
          "doc": "Size of available positions (width, height, 0)",
          "isOptional": false,
          "name": "available_size",
